OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe Borders
OL,6,Fand East Lothian will stay cloudy with
OL,7,Fsome patchy rain, perhaps becoming
OL,8,Fmore persistent overnight. The west
OL,9,Fwill be dry with some clear periods
OL,10,Fover Galloway.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FMostly cloudy with some
OL,13,Fpatchy rain, though more persistent at
OL,14,Ffirst over eastern Borders. Best of
OL,15,Fany brighter weather over Galloway.
OL,16,FColder, especially in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
