OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry with some sunny spells on Sunday,
OL,7,Fsome light rain in evening. Monday dry
OL,8,Fand bright, then some patchy evening
OL,9,Frain. Sunny spells and a few showers
OL,10,Fon Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
